Dialogue: 10,0:23:10.42,0:23:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! My memories are back!\NYou are all my friends!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:13.79,0:23:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Cook, swordsman, navigator,\Ndoctor, scholar, and... liar.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:16.38,0:23:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hey...\N--Well then, we'll go bring back Nami and Zoro!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:18.97,0:23:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally agree about Nami-san,\Nbut we don't need that man.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:20.97,0:23:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,--Right, we don't.\N--I guess we don't. No! We do!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:23.35,0:23:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't do without even one person!
